title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 358-2.24 - Title
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 358-2.24 - Title

State Regulations

Title means Title 18 of the New York State Official

Compilation of Codes, Rules and Regulations (NYCRR) also referred to as the
regulations of the Department of Family Assistance. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18
§§
358-2.24

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
